    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(0.51)
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.72) + (v0 + 0.81 * tmp + 0.11)) + (wp.exp(v0 + 0.42) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.73)))
    v2 = v1
